<emphasis bold="true" box="[172,281,3325,3359]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">Habitat.</emphasis>
Alpine scrub, shallow marshes, and boggy alpine heath at elevations of¢.2950 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
