<subSubSection pageId="241" pageNumber="846" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="241.[1456,2660,294,566]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1456,1808,338,367]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Arianus’s New Guinea Mountain Rat has a very restricted distribution, but it occurs in Lorentz National Park. More research is needed to fully understand its natural history and conservation threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
